reviewText: We love Beavis and Butt-head and needed to replace our VHS tape as it was wearing out!
There's only 8 episode on it... Those episodes don't last very long. I have no problem with the seller though.
These hi quality tapes are a must have, for the traditional movie goer. Nothing like an outstanding movie-anytime or any place!
This one is hilarious I just love Beavis and Butthead they never fail to make me laugh they are so entertaining and if you are fans of them like me you'll love this one!
funny dvd but 8 episodes goes bye in 25 mins lol. but has some funny episodes when they copy money was funny
No music videos like Beavis and Butthead of old. Dont waste your time and money on this product. Episodes are short,chopped up and everything is censored!
Fast shipping, brand new factory sealed, Great show, really funny. A collection of Beavis and Butt-head episodes trying to make a buck and music videos with their classic commentary.
